---
import Title from "../common/Title.astro";
import Button from "../common/Button.astro";
import AnimationBgHero from "../common/AnimationBgHero.astro";
---

<main
    class="relative flex flex-col items-center gap-4 py-8 sm:py-12 lg:py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 h-screen sm:overflow-hidden overflow-auto"
>
    <!-- Animated Wave Background -->
    <AnimationBgHero />

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="w-full max-w-5xl relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <Title size="2xl" />
            <h2
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center px-4"
            >
                Conecta Pacientes y Fisioterapeutas En Un Mismo Ecosistema
                Completo
            </h2>

            <p
                class="font-light text-sm sm:text-base text-center w-full sm:w-4/5 md:w-3/4 lg:w-2/3 xl:w-1/2 opacity-80 px-4"
            >
                MotionHub simplifica la gestión de citas, rutinas personalizadas
                y seguimiento del progreso. Una plataforma diseñada para
                fisioterapeutas y pacientes
            </p>

            <Button text="Comenzar →" href="#" theme="dark" />
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
